body:
Day 16 - Manga 351*
The guy has superpowers? Couldn't understand anything but it wasn't a totally bad read.
Some fetishes I didn't like, the scat one, for example.
Overall, a pretty solid manga that should be translated.
4/10 with the possibility to go higher.
So this is the first mind control doujinshi
Not the greatest sign when you see someone fucking hanging like that in the first few pages, 4/10
